text.en_US: Another strange visitor has arrived at the roots.
text.zh_CN: 又一位异域来客回归故里。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/10/13]
text.ko_KR: 낯선 방문객이 또 한 명 아래에 도착했군.<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/10/17]
text.ja_JP: これはまた奇妙な客が根に到着したようだな。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/11/04]
text.zh_TW: 又一位異域來客回歸故里。<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/10/13]

text.en_US: One trying to reach the top of Krys'kajo as well?
text.pt_BR: Você está tentando alcançar o topo do Krys'kajo também?
text.de_DE: Wird einer versuchen, auch das Dach des Krys'kajo zu erreichen?
text.zh_CN: 想要到达凯斯卡罗的顶部吗？
text.ja_JP: 汝もまた、クリュス・カーヨの頂点を目指す者か？
text.zh_TW: 想要到達凱斯卡羅的頂部嗎？

text.en_US: One needs to prove the mastery of \c[3]Shock\c[0] and \c[3]Wave\c[0] for one to ascend.
text.pt_BR: Sabe minha chapinha, você precisa provar o domínio do \c[3]Choque\c[0] e \c[3]Onda\c[0] para ascender.
text.de_DE: Um dorthin aufzusteigen, wird einer die Meisterschaft von \c[3]Welle\c[0] und \c[3]Schock\c[0] unter Beweis stellen müssen.
text.zh_CN: 想要上去，就需要证明自己对\c[3]波\c[0]与\c[3]电\c[0]的掌控力。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
text.ja_JP: もし登ろうというのなら、\c[3]波動\c[0]と\c[3]電撃\c[0]のエレメントに精通している必要がある。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
text.zh_TW: 想要上去，就需要證明自己對\c[3]波\c[0]與\c[3]電\c[0]的掌控力。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]

text.en_US: I shall watch this one closely.
text.de_DE: Ich werde ihn im Auge behalten.
text.ja_JP: 汝のことは注意深く見ておこう。

message.en_US: Ape Guy!! Did you meet the ape guy?
message.pt_BR: Macaco!! Vocês já viram o macaco?
message.de_DE: Affenmensch!! Seid ihr dem Affenmenschen begegnet?
message.zh_CN: 猴子！你遇到那个猴子了吗？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
サル男！ねえ、
サル男に会った？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 猴子！你遇到那個猴子了嗎？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Also, what is this? Wasn't this supposed to be a race?
message.pt_BR: E o que é isso? Isso não era pra ser uma corrida?
message.de_DE: Was wird das hier? Sollte das nicht ein Rennen sein?<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_CN: 还有这是干嘛？我们不是在比赛吗？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP:
その前にこの通信はなんだ？
俺たちは競争してるんじゃ
なかったのか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ko_KR: 근데 이건 뭐야? 우리 시합하는 거 아니었나?<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 還有這是幹嘛？我們不是在比賽嗎？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

message.pt_BR: Então porque está usando o D-Link?
message.ja_JP:
じゃあ、なぜ
ダイレクトリンクを使う？<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Why not? It doesn't hurt to have a few breaks in between.
message.pt_BR: Por que não? Não custa nada ter algumas pausas.
message.de_DE: Warum nicht? Ein paar kleine Pausen zwischendurch können nicht schaden.
message.zh_CN: 有何不可？打累了休息一下嘛。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
使っちゃダメなの？
途中で少し休憩するくらい
問題ないでしょ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 뭐 어때? 사이사이에 잠깐 쉰다고 해가 되진 않는걸.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 有何不可？打累了休息一下嘛。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.de_DE: Wir haben doch gerade erst angefangen!
message.ja_JP:
競争をはじめてから
そう経っていないだろう！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 우리 시작한 지 얼마 안 됐잖아!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Oui, but I had to talk about the ape!
message.pt_BR: Oui, mas tinha que falar do macaco!
message.de_DE: Oui, aber ich musste mit euch über den Affenmenschen reden!
message.zh_CN: 但那个猴子我非聊不可！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
ウィ、でもサルについて
話したくて！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 그래, 하지만 유인원에 관한 대화를 나누고 싶어!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 但那個猴子我非聊不可！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.ja_JP: サルって面白いでしょ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: This ape oversees every Seeker that enters this place.
message.pt_BR: Este macaco observa cada Seeker que entra neste lugar.
message.de_DE: Dieser Affe überwacht jeden Seeker, der diesen Ort betritt.
message.zh_CN: 这猿猴监察每一个进入这里的探索者。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
あのサルはここに足を踏み入れた
探索者すべてを見張っているんだぞ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 이 유인원은 이곳에 들어오는 모든 시커를 지켜보지.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 這猿猴監察每一個進入這裡的探索者。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: It's a mysterious yet honorable creature of ancient origin.
message.pt_BR: É uma criatura misteriosa mas honrada, de origem antiga.
message.de_DE: Eine mysteriöse, aber ehrenwerte Kreatur aus alter Zeit.
message.ja_JP:
いにしえに起源を持つ、
神秘的で高貴な生き物なんだ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: So? I still think it's funny!
message.pt_BR: E dai? Eu ainda acho ele engraçado!
message.de_DE: Na und? Ich find' ihn trotzdem lustig!
message.ja_JP:
そう？でも面白いと
思うけどな！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Fine, then. Let's properly start the race, already.
message.pt_BR: Muito bem, então. Vamos começar a corrida de forma adequada, já.
message.de_DE: Wie du meinst. Nun lasst uns aber endlich mit dem Rennen beginnen.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_CN: 好吧。让我们继续比赛吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ja_JP:
もういい。さっさとレースを
開始しようじゃないか。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.zh_TW: 好吧。讓我們繼續比賽吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
